leve.name: Not Losing Our Heads This Time
leve.description: The Stone Vigil will be won by solving deadly puzzles we could not at the last battle. One such cipher is how to send runners and supplies while dodging the wyverns' barbed tails and fiery breaths. The answer is that we do not dodge, we dig. Study the earth well, for we mean to sink our trenches deep.
leve.client: House Durendaire Knight, Brunadier of the Blue Bell
